  Chai7 Tiong-kok a2-si7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 hian7-si5 sou2-u7 e5 chong-kau3 chiu7-si7 Put8-kau3, Hoe5-hoe5-kau3, Ia5-sou-kau3. Chit kui2-cheng2 m7-si7 Han3-bin5-chok8 sou2 chhong3-siat--e5 , long2 si7 tui3 Goa7-kok thoan5-lai5--e5 . Chaih-e5 chu7 thoan5 lai5 Tiong-kok i2-au7 m7-na7 bo5 khah hoat-tat8 , tian-to3 si7 u7 khah hun7-loan7 the3-pou7 e5 khoan2-iuN7. Han3-bin5-chok8 ka-ti7 bo5 chhong3-siat chong-kau3 . Koh-chai3 tui3 pat8-tah thoan5--e5 ia7 be7 thang khah hoat-tat8, chit-hang7 ia7 chiu7 chiok-giah8 thang cheng3-beng5 Han3-chok8 si7 tiong7 sit8-chai7 , tiong7 hian7-si5 bak8-chiu-cheng5 e5 tai7-chi3 , bo5 siuN7 koan-sim ti7 chiong-lai5 eng2-kiu2 e5 kui-kiok8 . Hoan7-na7 khah hng7 khah bi5-biau2 e5 chiu7 khah bo5 chhu3-bi7 e5 khoan2-sit. Sou2-i2 in sou2 hi-bong7--e5 chiu7-si7 Chai5, Chu2, Siu7 . Sou2 ka3-si7 sou2 gi7-lun7 e5 chiu7-si7 siu-sin, che5-ka , ti7-kok , peng5 thian-ha7 hit-khoan2 sit8-sit8 chai7-chai7 e5 tai7-chi3. 
